{"tid":2457121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇留意哂，香港本地音樂、電影、足球係咪都多人睇左","createTime":"2021-03-22T11:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T12:05:29.000Z","uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9398e2d464137cf1f8c7e01a3fb662e7535a5209","tid":2457121,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"最大感覺係音樂<br />\n而家真係好左好多人聽廣東歌<br />\n新一代歌手仲好撚有實力下<br />\n我覺得擺脫左早5-10年嗰個低潮期<br />\n<br />\n電影我唔知叫唔叫好左<br />\n不過今日一秒拳王係單日票房冠軍<br />\n狂舞派3 收 7,911,653<br />\n我唔知點去理解呢個數字<br />\n大致上同神奇女俠1984差唔多<br />\n3月電影票房排第4<br />\n<br />\n足球好似都有撲飛潮<br />\n雖然話開得一半<br />\n但就咁睇氣氛都幾好<br />\n<br />\n香港本土野係咪多左人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c6bf5a9158926f852ecbfe7083b7e328938f45","tid":2457121,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:37:36.000Z","msg":"gem一直都好多人聽"},{"pid":"028df297db67c8f935cd009ff1c042882dba65d4","tid":2457121,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"香港本土歌影視業一定要重新復興，新一代歌手台前演員台後工作人員編劇導演都要為香港鑄造新一個盛世，為港爭光"},{"pid":"cdfbbfca40d8c11a34aa85ee07c30d661b62345d","tid":2457121,"uid":85864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c6bf5a9158926f852ecbfe7083b7e328938f45","tid":2457121,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:37:36.000Z","msg":"gem一直都好多人聽"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"who<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n造星個啲定係咩蚊型公司既新人？"},{"pid":"7e400f8dbc883f5a081ba45fdbabd479919cf83b","tid":2457121,"uid":304435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdfbbfca40d8c11a34aa85ee07c30d661b62345d","tid":2457121,"uid":85864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c6bf5a9158926f852ecbfe7083b7e328938f45","tid":2457121,"uid":